    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Throwing clubs with a short shaft and a large heavy knob at one end, originating in southern Africa and typically made of hardwood.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
